{"tid":551990,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"沾麵","createTime":"2018-02-06T06:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T06:17:09.000Z","uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7621a08a0a53b18397d417e767cef3fc67d309fb","tid":551990,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"開業初期俾人屌佢湯底鹹<br />\n唔知係咪佢地自己調整左<br />\n我今日食就完全唔覺<br />\n反而覺得濃多少少更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實已經唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麵唔夠爽身<br />\n麵質無周月咁好<br />\n不過都算有咬口<br />\n應該唔會差過富士山55/mk漁場台風<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/145817_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F145817_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=73d30197&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"842daff1c7a252036d48f1b3e65951c31b9e0886","tid":551990,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:21:42.000Z","msg":"去咗旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e77092bc05704b862ebf55aec001259c9b2a52a","tid":551990,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去咗旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09952ca3e4af4855bbeb3ad122365957f3cdfd45","tid":551990,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去咗旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到咁靚 以為你去咗旅行"},{"pid":"d3311dc91a2e7506de7d3e795758999bf6d0a624","tid":551990,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"紅色個兜咩黎？"},{"pid":"834a8a9bed1d76b31dc728628e744cc2a44631d5","tid":551990,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09952ca3e4af4855bbeb3ad122365957f3cdfd45","tid":551990,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去咗旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到咁靚 以為你去咗旅行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"你食撚屎啦，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eede9edf868267b9d32b92c9a5bfef4d660c5d69","tid":551990,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅色個兜咩黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似話係櫻花蝦辣魚介粉<br />\n食到最尾加左d落湯試下<br />\n感覺一般"},{"pid":"91187a1dfaae45ffbc37ca8b47a163ac166dfb55","tid":551990,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"我鍾意周月多啲，麵質更好。個人口味。"},{"pid":"25393a988990e42f61227ac88cebe2bbe75ba621","tid":551990,"uid":136097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"得兩塊咁細既肉?"},{"pid":"0b448e23bb3a1af834f70dd28ec3c3573c0aca46","tid":551990,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鍾意周月多啲，麵質更好。個人口味。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有一年無去周月喇<br />\n麵質真係同香港其他既唔同層次<br />\n我接受到佢浸怪味喎<br />\n幾鍾意佢獨特既魚香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8833666fc68da07190ffb1cb812edd381fed762","tid":551990,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得兩塊咁細既肉?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n另有兩粒肉丸喺湯入面<br />\n幾鍾意佢舊雞肉"},{"pid":"cbeaeb88752055935403241d6264b334ee1f7f58","tid":551990,"uid":138155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"睇落唔錯 但係真係太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 168蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c97c6682bbec6c7f48748cf3f12a0bbd3c6de4c","tid":551990,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"有冇東京雞飯？"},{"pid":"b58d68cc8187e18e15f42b5620bb565ebdc3007e","tid":551990,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbeaeb88752055935403241d6264b334ee1f7f58","tid":551990,"uid":138155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"睇落唔錯 但係真係太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 168蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0359ef6cd505d65d82bc2381700564506eda25e","tid":551990,"uid":7079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"好食係好食<br />\n但唔值$150-170<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9641d9112e708928e54d55327f37ebb2fdb65f87","tid":551990,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T13:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇落唔錯 但係真係太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 168蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n158<im